LEFT JOIN [Items] AS [i0] ON [c].[ID] = [i0].[CartID]
WHERE [s].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
ORDER BY [s].[DateCreated] DESC, [s].[ID], [i].[ID], [c].[ID], [i0].[ID]"
